text: The @GlobalShapers of the #Yaound hub are a good looking bunch, wouldn't you say? Are you still interested in joining us? If yes, stay tuned for a special announcement from the @YaoundeShapers within the next 24 hours!//t.co/LVd4Q9OpKN

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: Good morning & happy Sunday from the @GlobalShapers of the Yaounde city. Few days left to apply to join a network of energetic youths contributing to community development in Yaounde & #Cameroon as a whole. See link below and reach out if any questions //t.co/THL1rUbrYF//t.co/IvLQFMn05N

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: Hello Yaound! We are looking for dynamic young people who are committed to improving the state of their community. Are you between 20 and 29 years old? Join us by registering on the following forms://t.co/THL1rUbrYF//t.co/HxpkRxPPmE #recrutement #Yaounde//t.co/BIK7LpVgCf

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: Thank you so much @CRTV_web for having us this morning on "Hello" to discuss the ongoing @GlobalShapers #Yaounde's recruitment drive. Only six days left! Applications close on March 25th at 11:59PM. If are you between 20-29 and want to join, apply today://t.co/HxpkRxPPmE//t.co/YiVmHzYdoq

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: Live from Cameroon National TV @CRTV_web, @GlobalShapers member of the #Yaound hub speaks on the importance of commitment. "Once recruited new shapers are on a three-month probation before getting officially approved in the hub."//t.co/MuYkMIEB5K

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: "The @YaoundeShapers are a team of incredibly committed and motivated young leaders who want to emerge through values. Over the last few months we implemented projects around solidarity, civic engagement and mentorship for younger generations."//t.co/hMVE2ElrKI

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: The @GlobalShapers of the #Yaound hub went on @CRTV_web's National Radio today to discuss @YaoundeShapers recruitment drive, encouraging eligible candidates to apply. Join a dynamic and lively group of Cameroonians committed to making a positive impact in Yaound and beyond.//t.co/mJMfqQqqja

text: #CNNStartupHelp Another way to overcome failure is to think about the impact your product/solution will have in your community by changing

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp you will always bounce back.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp Chase your vision and think about it about everyday and work hard to achieve, during difficult times think about it, and

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp It is the reasons every entrepreneur should a clear and vivid vision or dream he/she has to achieve,

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp Until it is achieved we will always stand up and bounce back

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp the vision to always put the best technology at the service of Africa to create a billion impact in 10 years,

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp For MyAconnect, we always bounce back and will always do so until our vision is achieved,

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp When facing failures always ask to yourself in your solitude moments WHY? Why I am doing it? Why did I fail?

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp I consider Perseverance as a quality suitable for those who understand that failure is a must to succeed.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp Challenges, setbacks, failure make life interesting, overcoming them through resilience and perseverance gives it meaning.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp True human development is to make perseverance, humility, confidence in oneself and the right to error personal values

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp over time especially as to face failure or resolutely pursue our objective means to be ready to start back again.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp This is a quality that possess in common all the people that have experienced success whose impact is still palpable

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp For me perseverance is a key virtue for those who really want to achieve sustainable success in all aspects of life.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp Those who fail are,for the most part,those who had not realized they were on the verge of success,be realistic,never give up

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp my advice is whatever happens,believe in life,believe in tomorrow believe in what you do,but especially,believe in yourself.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp Everything is possible for that dream, that dares, works and most important never gives up

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp For me failure is not bad, but an important step to take to him who believes in himself and is voluntary to succeed

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp Eveyday i say to myself that I can accept failure, everyone may fail. But I cannot accept not trying.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp I always take failure as an offered opportunity to better hone the combat arms for success.

name: FABRICE ALOMO
text: #CNNStartupHelp For me Failure is the opportunity to begin again more intelligently
